In the @minnkotamotors Unlock the Lake, Tommy Sanders and @ronniemoorebass go through some of the top competitors and how/where they were successful for the final stop of the 2021 Bassmaster Elite Series season. With Lake Ontario being open to anglers, we saw at least half the Top 10 make the run to that region of upstate New York York. 
#Bassmaster #BASSElite #BassFishing #StLawrenceRiver

node.title: Finding the Top areas at the St. Lawrence/Ontario (Unlock the Lake)

#Bassmaster #BassFishing #PeakPerformance

In today's #TackleTipTuesday video brought to you by @mercurymarine, @takumiitou4663 breaks down his keys to success at the St. Lawrence River. He heavily relies on scents and smells when smallmouth fishing. So he soaks his baits in Nories scent juice in Tupperware containers. This allows the baits to soak in the smell and attract smallmouth to bite better. 
#Bassmaster #BassFishing #BASSElite
